<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Create New User - IT Admin Portal</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif; }
        .valid-req { color: #059669 !important; font-weight: 700; } 
        .valid-req i { color: #059669 !important; }
        .valid-req i::before { content: "\f00c"; } 
        .invalid-req { color: #94a3b8; }
        .invalid-req i { color: #cbd5e1; }
        .error-req { color: #ef4444 !important; font-weight: 700; }
        .error-req i { color: #ef4444 !important; }
        .error-req i::before { content: "\f00d"; } 
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <nav class="bg-slate-900 text-white shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-3">
            <a href="/" class="text-lg font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-slate-200 transition w-fit">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> กลับหน้าหลัก
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10 flex-grow flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="w-full max-w-3xl">
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 px-8 py-6 text-white">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus bg-white/20 p-2 rounded-lg"></i> 
                        สร้างผู้ใช้งานใหม่ (Create User)
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-emerald-50 text-sm mt-2 ml-1 opacity-90">กรอกข้อมูลเพื่อเพิ่มพนักงานลงใน Active Directory</p>
                </div>

                <div class="p-8">
                    <form action="/users/create" method="POST" class="space-y-6" id="createForm">
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">ชื่อจริง (First Name) <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400"><i class="fa-regular fa-user"></i></span>
                                    <input type="text" name="firstName" required placeholder="สมชาย"
                                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">นามสกุล (Last Name) <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                                <input type="text" name="lastName" required placeholder="ใจดี"
                                    class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Username (สำหรับ Login) <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                            <div class="relative group">
                                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400 group-focus-within:text-emerald-600 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-desktop"></i></span>
                                <input type="text" name="username" id="usernameInput" placeholder="เช่น somchai.j" required 
                                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white font-medium text-slate-700">
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1.5 ml-1">ใช้ภาษาอังกฤษตัวพิมพ์เล็กเท่านั้น</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">อีเมล (Email)</label>
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400"><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i></span>
                                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="user@biccorp.com"
                                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">แผนก (Department)</label>
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400"><i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i></span>
                                    <input type="text" name="department" placeholder="เช่น IT, HR, Sales"
                                        class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
                            <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">
                                จัดเก็บในหน่วยงาน (OU Location) <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                            </label>
                            <div class="relative group">
                                <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400 group-focus-within:text-emerald-600 transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-sitemap"></i>
                                </span>
                                <select name="ouDN" class="w-full pl-10 pr-10 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-white focus:bg-white appearance-none cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium">
                                    <option value="">-- ค่าเริ่มต้น (Users Default) --</option>
                                    
                                    <% if (typeof ous !== 'undefined' && ous.length > 0) { %>
                                        <% ous.forEach(function(ou) { %>
                                            <option value="<%= ou %>"><%= ou.split(',')[0].replace('OU=', '') %></option>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    <% } %>
                                </select>
                                
                                <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-4 flex items-center pointer-events-none text-slate-400">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-xs"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 ml-1 flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info text-emerald-500"></i> เลือกแผนกใน AD ที่ต้องการจัดเก็บ User นี้
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 mt-4">
                            <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 mt-4">กำหนดรหัสผ่าน <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                            
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                <div>
                                    <div class="relative">
                                        <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center text-slate-400"><i class="fa-solid fa-key"></i></span>
                                        <input type="password" name="password" id="passwordInput" required onkeyup="checkPassword()" placeholder="ตั้งรหัสผ่าน..."
                                            class="w-full pl-10 pr-24 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none transition bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white font-medium">
                                        
                                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <button type="button" onclick="generatePassword()" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-600 transition outline-none p-1" title="สุ่มรหัสผ่านอัตโนมัติ">
                                                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i>
                                            </button>
                                            
                                            <span class="w-px h-4 bg-slate-300"></span>

                                            <button type="button" onclick="togglePassword()" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 transition outline-none p-1">
                                                <i class="fa-regular fa-eye" id="eyeIcon"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2 ml-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info mr-1"></i> ใช้สำหรับ Login ครั้งแรก</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm text-slate-600 shadow-sm">
                                    <p class="font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved mr-1.5"></i> Password Strength
                                    </p>
                                    <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs font-medium transition-all">
                                        <li id="req-length" class="flex items-start gap-2 invalid-req transition-colors duration-300">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle mt-1 text-[8px]"></i> <span>ความยาวอย่างน้อย 8 ตัวอักษร</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li id="req-complex" class="flex items-start gap-2 invalid-req transition-colors duration-300">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle mt-1 text-[8px]"></i> <span>มี A-Z, a-z และ 0-9 ผสมกัน</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li id="req-user" class="flex items-start gap-2 invalid-req transition-colors duration-300">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle mt-1 text-[8px]"></i> <span>ไม่ใช้ชื่อ User เป็นส่วนประกอบ</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-6 flex items-center justify-end gap-3 mt-6">
                            <a href="/" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 font-medium transition duration-200">
                                ยกเลิก
                            </a>
                            <button type="submit" id="submitBtn" disabled class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-white bg-slate-400 cursor-not-allowed font-bold shadow-md transition duration-200">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-check mr-2"></i>ยืนยันการสร้าง
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/createUser.js"></script>

</body>
</html>